46
00:02:36,180 --> 00:02:38,640
That data includes your username,

47
00:02:38,640 --> 00:02:41,129
what you like, where you are in the world,

48
00:02:41,129 --> 00:02:42,599
what’s being recorded by your

49
00:02:42,599 --> 00:02:46,200
